                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100411-119-defend1012 t18100411-119-deflabel678"></join> and so employed, did receive and take into his possession the sum of 3 s. 9 1/2 d. for on account of his said master and that he feloniously did secrete and steal the same
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18100411-119-person1014">
